## Cluster Boot order
### Startup
  1. Manager nodes
  2. Admin nodes
  3. Login nodes
  4. Compute nodes

### Shutdown
  1. Compute nodes
  2. Login nodes
  3. Admin nodes
  4. Manager nodes


