### Shell timeout and lock
  - Edit /etc/profile.d/tmout.sh
  TMOUT=900
  readonly TMOUT
  export TMOUT

  yum install vlock

### Prelink
  - Edit /etc/sysconfig/prelink:
  PRELINKING=no
  /usr/sbin/prelink -ua

